   FREMONT, Calif. -- Sigma Designs Inc. said profit for the
fiscal-first quarter ended April 30 was "significantly below"
the $1.6 million, or 27 cents a share, reported for the
fiscal-fourth quarter ended Jan. 31.
   Sales of approximately $10 million fell below the $12
