</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE C21
</SO>
<CO>
   GQ
</CO>
<IN>
AEROSPACE (ARO)
BOND MARKET NEWS (BON)
STOCK MARKET, OFFERINGS (STK)
</IN>
<LP>
   Moody's Investors Service Inc. said it downgraded its
ratings on $525 million of Grumman Corp.'s senior and
subordinated debt and preferred stock.
   The rating of Grumman's senior and subordinated debt fell
to Baa-3 from Baa-2 and to Ba-2 from Baa-3, respectively. The
rating of its preferred stock dropped to Ba-2 from Baa-3.
</LP>
