<LP>
   Investor Norman Elowitz said he may make a new offer to
acquire Ultimate Corp., an East Hanover, N.J.,
computer-products concern.
   In a filing with the Securities and Exchange Commission,
Mr. Elowitz, chairman of Honey Fashions Ltd., also said he
